stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Running: executor dispatches step
    Running --> Success: body returned
    Running --> Failed: exception raised
    Failed --> Backoff: attempts remaining
    Backoff --> Running: retry_delay elapsed
    Failed --> OnFailure: retries exhausted<br>on_failure defined
    Failed --> StepFailed: retries exhausted<br>no on_failure
    OnFailure --> StepFailed: cleanup ran<br>error re-raised
    Success --> [*]
    StepFailed --> [*]
